<p>
<strong>MCK (09-01-05)</strong>: Don't know if it's worth asking here, but I've noticed that both Air and Antimagic realms give access to "add to speed" powers.  If the RNG blesses you and grants you this power from both realms, is it cumulative?  For that matter, is it even possible to get both of them? 
</p>
<p>
<strong><a href="./ScrawnyCat">ScrawnyCat</a></strong>: Not cumulative. It's the same power, only in multiple realms. You can't get it more than once. I'd be more happy to get extra blows twice if it was possible, by the way (from antimagic and earth). 
</p>

                <ul>

    <strong>MCK</strong>: Good point.  Thanks <strong><a href="./ScrawnyCat">ScrawnyCat</a></strong>! </ul>

